My favorite cheesecake..I'm not fond of dense, heavy cheesecake or overly sweet desserts. I use the entire can of pumpkin (closer to 2 cups), use 3 T of flour instead of cornstarch, organic sucanat instead of white and brown sugar, 1 1/4 C gingersnaps and half the sugar for the crust, and bake it in a 10" pan. To be time and space efficient, I throw all the filling ingredients in a blender.

